data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 1 acre, 2,016sqft  farm house just west of Spencerville High School. This property would make the perfect place for someone wanting that cozy country living. This home features ample amount of space, gorgeous hardwood floors, updated windows, updated kitchen, updated bathrooms, four covered parking areas and many more features! Be sure to check it out!
